      <div class="headliner__details headliner-one__info">
        <div class="category category--headliner category--breaking">
          <p>Breaking</p>
        </div>
        <h2 class="headliner__title">
          Local Hero Chester the Cat Becomes First Feline Board Member at
          Hometown ASPCA
        </h2>
        <p class="headliner__excerpt">
          Me-ow! Beloved cat Chester becomes the first of his species on the
          local ASPCA board. When asked for a comment, Chester slowly walked
          away, stopped, turned back to us, then kept walking.
        </p>
        <a class="headliner__link" href="/posts">Read More...</a>
      </div>
      <div class="headliner__details headliner-two">
        <div class="headliner__img-wrapper">
          <img src="https://i.imgur.com/35QDIiF.jpeg" alt="" class="headliner__img" />
