            <p>Events</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <h2 class="headliner__title">
          County Fair Will Draw Thousands
        </h2>
      </div>
      <div class="headliner__details headliner-three">
        <div class="headliner__img-wrapper">
          <img src="https://i.imgur.com/wYTCtRu.jpeg" alt="" class="headliner__img" />
          <div class="category category--headliner category--community">
            <p>Community</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <h2 class="headliner__title">Celebrating Marie's 100th Birthday</h2>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="articles">
      <div class="article">
        <img class="article__img" src="https://i.imgur.com/0LINzxs.jpeg" alt="" />
        <div class="category category--article category--politics">
          <p>Politics</p>
        </div>
        <div class="article__info">
          <h2 class="article__title">
            Mayor Brandy & Mayor Grant Approve High-Speed Rail Plans
          </h2>
          <p class="article__excerpt">
            The mayors of Hometown and Statesville have been awarded a grant to
            build and connect a high-speed rail between the towns.
          </p>
          <a class="article__link" href="/posts">Read More...</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="article">
        <img class="article__img" src="https://i.imgur.com/xGmX4h3.jpeg" alt="" />
        <div class="article__info">
          <div class="category category--article category--events">
            <p>Events</p>
          </div>
          <h2 class="article__title">
            Road Trip Meetups Through Hometown County
          </h2>
          <p class="article__excerpt">
            Pack your bags, baby! It’s time to head on an exciting road trip
            with a few Hometown County neighbors! Check out local road trip
            meetups here.
          </p>
          <a class="article__link" href="/posts">Read More...</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="article">
        <img class="article__img" src="https://i.imgur.com/wkqgWyO.jpeg" alt="" />
