          <div class="category category--article category--sports">
            <p>Sports</p>
          </div>
          <h2 class="article__title">Hometown Hawks Win 31 - 20</h2>
          <p class="article__excerpt">
            Hometown Hawks swooped in with a 4th-quarter victory against Old
            Country Village. This is the third win for the Hawks, giving them a
            chance at going to State. Ca-caw!
          </p>
          <a class="article__link" href="/posts">Read More...</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="article">
        <img class="article__img" src="https://i.imgur.com/PAHiKxN.jpeg" alt="" />
        <div class="article__info">
