            <p>Politics</p>
          </div>
          <h2 class="article__title">
            Municipal Voting Shows Highest Recorded Turn Out!
          </h2>
          <p class="article__excerpt">
            We got out the vote! More than 85% of registered voters turned out
            at this municipal election, approving some measures and turning down
            an unpopular ban on chewing gum.
          </p>
          <a class="article__link" href="/posts">Read More...</a>
